des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Olfabrand products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Olfabrand" app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our "Olfabrand" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search "Olfabrand" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable "Olfabrand" skill, and you'll be navigated to "Olfabrand" login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on diffuser.
Alexa, turn off diffuser.
Alexa, turn on light on diffuser.
Alexa, turn off light on diffuser.
Alexa, is light on for diffuser?
Alexa, turn on spray on diffuser.
Alexa, turn off spray on diffuser.
Alexa, is spray on for diffuser?
